<p>This time, the view box only covers the top left-hand corner.</p>

<p>In addition, I’ve found out that changing <code class="highlighter-rouge">0 0 400 200</code> to <code class="highlighter-rouge">400 200 0 0</code>
<em>doesn’t</em> work.</p>

